Name: urlfetch
Version: 0.2
Summary: An easy to use HTTP client based on httplib
Home-page: https://github.com/lyxint/urlfetch
Author: Elyes Du
Author-email: lyxint@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: urlfetch
        ========
        
        Description
        -----------
        An easy to use HTTP client based on httplib
        
        Installation
        -------------
        ::
            
            $ pip install urlfetch -U
        
        
        Hello World
        -----------
        ::
            
            from urlfetch import get
            
            response = get('http://python.org/')
            print response.body
        
        Upload file
        -----------
        ::
        
            from urlfetch import post
            response = post('http://127.0.0.1:8888/', files={'formname': open('/path/to/file', 'rb')})
            print response.reqheaders
            print response.body
        
